    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80dd-84b1-ce7471144a37",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Dataset uses 48602 logged events and 131 excerpts from student reflections. Segmentation is done on High-Performance vs Low-Performing students. High-Performing students exhibited SRL behaviours more frequently. ",
